data.description: Spacious home in Southern Oaks subdivision has been Freshly painted, hardwood floors with a large living room and dining room combination. The kitchen has white cabinets, tile floor, and tumbled stone back splash, with a breakfast area that open to the family room that features a Black and white  fireplace and a guest bedroom all on the 1st level. On the 2nd level there are 3 bedrooms, and a full hall bathroom,  a Spacious Master Suite with a Separate shower and an elevated garden/whirlpool tub located on a large corner lot, near Flat Shoals Parkway & Wesley Chapel Rd. The Kroger and Publix shopping center are just minutes away. The HVAC system and Hot water Heater are about 2 years old. This home is being Sold As is.   Must see!
